::Shadow Wing::

She flew back to the Ark.  She transformed at the entrance and walked 
in.  She went to engine room looking for Lunarpine.
She didn't see him so she went to his quarters.  He wasn't there 
either.  She went to the bridge. "Has anyone seen or heard from 
Lunarpine?"
